snippet.title: S.U.M.: Slay Uncool Monsters - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
What we have here is a puzzle game involving basic math, in an RPG setting.
Do you know your basic math skills enough to slay monsters?

S.U.M.: Slay Uncool Monsters (C) Doomster Entertainment
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1476430/SUM__Slay_Uncool_Monsters/
